de.rub.nds.burp.utilities

Class Logging

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rub.nds.burp.utilities.Logging

  • public class Logging
extends Object
    The extension internal logging.
    Version:
    1.0 ATTENTION!
    Based on the internal architecture of Burp Suite, the first called class is BurpExtender, this class initialises the PrintWriter. So NEVER call the Logging before this initialisation.
    Author:
    Tim Guenther
